WEBVTT

00:32.150 --> 00:33.750
Something is wrong with you.

00:34.860 --> 00:35.780
You said it yourself.

00:35.780 --> 00:37.140
Whenever we meet,

00:37.270 --> 00:38.950
we must not wait with our backs turned.

00:38.950 --> 00:40.460
We need to clearly see who is coming,

00:40.460 --> 00:43.460
if their condition is right,
and if they brought anyone.

00:43.460 --> 00:44.100
Yao.

00:44.910 --> 00:46.040
You broke the rules.

00:48.030 --> 00:48.860
I was wrong.

00:58.630 --> 00:59.070
Here.

00:59.350 --> 01:02.080
The backup
of Hengyun Logistics' latest ledger.

01:07.710 --> 01:08.840
What's on your mind?

01:10.630 --> 01:11.550
I came early

01:12.300 --> 01:13.630
and caught the sunrise.

01:14.710 --> 01:16.640
The morning sun rising in the east—

01:16.860 --> 01:18.660
I haven't seen it for a long time.

01:21.660 --> 01:22.550
My son's name

01:22.990 --> 01:23.990
is Xudong.

01:25.470 --> 01:26.350
Yao Xudong.

01:27.300 --> 01:28.910
Since when do you have a son?

01:30.380 --> 01:31.710
Eight years ago today,

01:32.910 --> 01:34.370
he died in the line of duty.

01:38.470 --> 01:39.550
He...

01:40.070 --> 01:41.110
was also a cop?

01:41.990 --> 01:42.920
A narcotics cop.

01:44.300 --> 01:46.229
He was killed by drug traffickers?

01:49.500 --> 01:51.710
He was tortured alive for 40 hours,

01:52.220 --> 01:53.680
wide awake the whole time,

01:54.220 --> 01:55.350
right until the end.

01:58.990 --> 02:00.830
By the time the police found him,

02:01.380 --> 02:02.140
his skull

02:02.630 --> 02:03.710
had been smashed,

02:04.990 --> 02:07.190
the skin on his legs had been peeled off,

02:07.910 --> 02:10.639
and there wasn't a single intact spot
on his body.

02:11.470 --> 02:13.270
I've never told anyone about it.

02:14.630 --> 02:16.890
We even used a pseudonym on his obituary.

02:19.700 --> 02:21.100
He was an undercover too?

02:23.030 --> 02:23.829
You know what?

02:25.750 --> 02:27.750
Before his last mission,

02:28.260 --> 02:29.870
he actually called me.

02:32.500 --> 02:34.070
He wanted me to get him

02:35.470 --> 02:37.660
one of those little cyanide capsules.

02:39.100 --> 02:40.960
He said the mission was dangerous

02:41.660 --> 02:43.520
and wanted to hide it in his tooth.

02:45.430 --> 02:47.160
In case he couldn't hold out...

02:49.750 --> 02:51.010
it might come in handy.

02:56.030 --> 02:57.100
I...

02:57.540 --> 02:58.590
scolded him.

03:08.980 --> 03:09.510
Maybe...

03:10.820 --> 03:11.750
Maybe...

03:12.940 --> 03:14.670
I should have gotten it for him.

03:20.190 --> 03:21.920
I should have done that for him.

03:25.350 --> 03:26.030
Yao,

03:27.430 --> 03:28.890
when this mission is over,

03:29.260 --> 03:30.590
I'll be your godson.

03:31.540 --> 03:32.430
Come on.

03:38.220 --> 03:40.420
Communist Party members don't do that.

03:42.470 --> 03:44.430
Then I'll go pay respect to him with you.

03:44.430 --> 03:45.260
Well...

03:45.260 --> 03:46.430
Where is he?

03:46.820 --> 03:47.540
Yunnan.

03:48.820 --> 03:49.260
Okay.

03:49.750 --> 03:51.210
I'll go to Yunnan with you.

03:58.430 --> 03:59.160
Jiang Cheng.

04:00.820 --> 04:02.550
The reason I'm telling you this

04:04.220 --> 04:05.500
is to let you know

04:06.700 --> 04:08.380
that the path you've chosen

04:10.940 --> 04:11.820
is really hard.

04:13.540 --> 04:15.430
No matter how prepared you are,

04:17.670 --> 04:19.940
reality might be much more dangerous.

04:23.310 --> 04:24.310
No matter how hard

04:24.900 --> 04:25.960
or dangerous it is,

04:26.940 --> 04:27.600
I accept it.

06:40.810 --> 06:46.430
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

06:46.780 --> 06:49.170
[Episode 22]

06:50.630 --> 06:51.960
From your perspective,

06:52.260 --> 06:53.860
why did you refuse to answer?

06:55.750 --> 06:57.820
Because you cared about his feelings.

06:57.820 --> 06:59.430
You were afraid of breaking his heart.

06:59.430 --> 07:00.560
What does that mean?

07:02.070 --> 07:02.750
It means

07:05.230 --> 07:06.960
you've fallen in love with him.

07:23.900 --> 07:26.380
But it seems I've messed everything up.

07:31.260 --> 07:33.500
It's not that complicated.

07:33.550 --> 07:35.190
As long as the love is still there,

07:35.190 --> 07:36.650
everything can be solved.

07:37.310 --> 07:38.570
Besides, it looks to me

07:38.580 --> 07:39.580
like Professor Jiang

07:39.580 --> 07:41.070
is more or less a hopeless romantic.

07:41.070 --> 07:42.470
He's very easy to handle.

07:44.580 --> 07:46.310
But you have to be careful.

07:46.990 --> 07:48.900
Professor Jiang is really outstanding.

07:48.900 --> 07:50.140
Everyone around us

07:50.260 --> 07:52.700
treats him like a treasure, right?

07:53.500 --> 07:54.670
When the Provincial Bureau leaders
came here,

07:54.670 --> 07:57.260
they wanted to poach him
as soon as they saw him.

07:57.260 --> 07:59.520
Why does Professor Jiang come to our unit

07:59.670 --> 08:00.310
every now and then?

08:00.310 --> 08:02.840
Could it be that he's interested
in Chief Tan?

08:08.820 --> 08:09.580
However,

08:10.140 --> 08:11.340
next time I see Professor Jiang,

08:11.340 --> 08:13.070
I must criticize him properly.

08:13.140 --> 08:15.310
He is still mostly to blame anyway.

08:15.380 --> 08:16.750
No matter how jealous

08:16.750 --> 08:18.380
or upset he was,
he shouldn't have mentioned divorce,

08:18.380 --> 08:19.790
let alone kicking you out.

08:19.790 --> 08:20.310
Right?

08:20.430 --> 08:21.020
Exactly.

08:21.260 --> 08:22.550
You should learn from me on this.

08:22.550 --> 08:23.900
If my husband dared to do this,

08:23.900 --> 08:25.580
I would have beaten him already.

08:25.580 --> 08:26.750
I yelled at him.

08:27.940 --> 08:28.940
I didn't dare to hit him.

08:28.940 --> 08:30.460
I was afraid he'd sue me
for domestic violence.

08:30.460 --> 08:31.190
Next time,

08:31.190 --> 08:33.070
just give him a shoulder throw.

08:33.390 --> 08:34.580
Throw him on the floor.

08:34.580 --> 08:35.309
Pin him down.

08:35.340 --> 08:36.789
That'll teach him a lesson
for mentioning divorce.

08:36.789 --> 08:37.789
I'm so mad, sis.

08:39.980 --> 08:41.150
I really am.

08:43.270 --> 08:45.330
Nothing really happened yesterday.

08:47.150 --> 08:48.390
He made me so furious

08:48.980 --> 08:50.640
that I barely slept all night.

08:51.910 --> 08:53.700
My mental state is terrible now.

08:53.700 --> 08:55.510
Then you should catch up on some sleep.

08:55.510 --> 08:56.430
I'll head to the unit first.

08:56.430 --> 08:57.560
Don't overthink it.

09:04.030 --> 09:04.890
One more thing.

09:05.740 --> 09:07.620
We contacted Zhao Ping's parents.

09:07.620 --> 09:08.950
But they refuse to come.

09:09.340 --> 09:10.100
They said

09:11.510 --> 09:13.970
they'd pretend
that they never had this son.

09:16.940 --> 09:17.620
People.

09:28.580 --> 09:29.340
Senior.

09:32.940 --> 09:34.740
I wanted to attend your wedding.

09:57.820 --> 10:00.030
You were kicked out by Jiang Hansheng?

10:02.820 --> 10:03.390
Really?

10:03.980 --> 10:05.740
Come on, tell me.

10:06.620 --> 10:07.190
Come on.

10:07.550 --> 10:09.550
What kind of problem is so serious

10:09.550 --> 10:10.860
that you two are separated?

10:10.860 --> 10:12.860
Does Jiang Hansheng
have some weird quirks?

10:12.860 --> 10:14.510
If there's something wrong with him,
don't just put up with it.

10:14.510 --> 10:16.270
What's that popular phrase now?

10:16.270 --> 10:17.460
Say no to emotional drain.

10:17.460 --> 10:18.270
Jiang Cheng.

10:18.580 --> 10:19.780
What are you here for?

10:20.030 --> 10:21.160
If there's nothing,

10:21.820 --> 10:22.700
you can leave now.

10:22.700 --> 10:24.150
Of course there is.

10:25.220 --> 10:25.980
Jin,

10:25.980 --> 10:28.340
I think marriage is a lifelong matter.

10:28.340 --> 10:30.190
If it's not working out,
just get a divorce.

10:30.190 --> 10:30.860
Get out!

10:34.860 --> 10:36.940
We grew up together, didn't we?

10:37.270 --> 10:38.940
You don't like me now.

10:38.940 --> 10:40.740
I accept that.

10:41.670 --> 10:43.130
Even if we are not a couple,

10:44.070 --> 10:45.790
I can still be considered your brother,
right?

10:45.790 --> 10:46.740
That guy Jiang Hansheng,

10:46.740 --> 10:48.310
I've always felt something was wrong
with him since we were kids.

10:48.310 --> 10:49.460
Stop talking.

10:50.510 --> 10:52.710
I know exactly what kind of person he is.

10:54.070 --> 10:55.930
Don't badmouth him in front of me.

10:56.220 --> 10:57.150
Okay, fine.

10:57.460 --> 10:58.520
I'll stop talking.

10:59.270 --> 11:00.940
Officer Jiang, there you are.

11:01.100 --> 11:02.340
Everything is ready over there.

11:02.340 --> 11:03.470
We can head over now.

11:04.030 --> 11:04.580
Zhou Jin,

11:04.910 --> 11:06.070
Chief Tan heard you were here too.

11:06.070 --> 11:07.390
He asked you to come along.

11:07.390 --> 11:09.270
Okay, I'll get changed and be right there.

11:09.270 --> 11:09.790
Okay.

11:26.610 --> 11:29.030
[Director Wang Pengze]
[Hansheng is with me.]

11:36.340 --> 11:38.270
You had an argument with your wife,

11:38.670 --> 11:39.740
and now you're here

11:39.740 --> 11:41.580
bothering an old man like me?

11:41.820 --> 11:42.910
Hurry up and eat.

11:55.720 --> 11:56.460
[Hansheng is with me.]

11:56.460 --> 11:57.190
[Mr. Wang, sorry for the trouble.
I had a misunderstanding]

11:57.190 --> 11:57.930
[with Hansheng. I'll go pick him up
when he's in a better mood.]

12:04.860 --> 12:05.700
Please read.

12:07.310 --> 12:07.970
Professor!

12:08.980 --> 12:09.910
How could you...

12:13.790 --> 12:15.980
I've got all this gray hair now.

12:16.550 --> 12:17.580
Don't bother me anymore.

12:16.770 --> 12:18.610
[Mr. Wang, sorry for the trouble.
I had a misunderstanding]

12:18.340 --> 12:20.820
It's normal for couples to argue.

12:18.610 --> 12:20.460
[with Hansheng. I'll go pick him up
when he's in a better mood.]

12:21.620 --> 12:23.700
Even the tongue and teeth sometimes clash.

12:23.700 --> 12:24.830
Whatever happened,

12:25.030 --> 12:26.310
let bygones be bygones.

12:26.310 --> 12:27.980
Don't be so hard on yourself.

12:28.120 --> 12:31.410
[Mr. Wang, sorry for the trouble.
I had a misunderstanding
with Hansheng. I'll go pick him up
when he's in a better mood.]

12:29.070 --> 12:31.070
A woman needs to be coaxed.

12:31.070 --> 12:32.620
I'm telling you,
you can't just ignore her.

12:32.620 --> 12:35.080
If you ignore her,
her love for you will fade.

12:35.190 --> 12:35.940
Chopsticks.

12:40.270 --> 12:43.800
There're just a few lines. Why have you
been reading for so long?

12:44.510 --> 12:45.790
Stop reading.

12:45.790 --> 12:46.910
Here.

12:48.100 --> 12:49.900
Professor Jiang. Please enjoy.

12:52.790 --> 12:53.700
Here.

13:03.460 --> 13:05.430
Look at how pathetic you are.

13:13.860 --> 13:14.790
Come in.

13:20.430 --> 13:22.030
I've read your psychological evaluation

13:22.030 --> 13:23.160
and medical report.

13:23.270 --> 13:24.550
There's no major problem.

13:24.550 --> 13:26.150
You can still take some hits.

13:26.310 --> 13:28.170
Then am I allowed to do fieldwork?

13:28.700 --> 13:29.900
Wait a little longer.

13:33.310 --> 13:33.940
Chief Tan.

13:36.620 --> 13:37.270
Not bad.

13:39.190 --> 13:40.850
We need you to help us identify

13:41.150 --> 13:42.270
the personnel related to Hengyun Logistics

13:42.270 --> 13:45.150
and the Kuangshan drug factory.

13:46.150 --> 13:46.820
No problem.

13:53.860 --> 13:55.460
Number 1, Number 2, Number 4.

13:55.820 --> 13:56.820
The rest are fine.

13:57.100 --> 13:58.430
Bring in the next group.

14:05.820 --> 14:06.880
Number 4, Number 7.

14:07.430 --> 14:08.760
Bring in the next group.

14:13.460 --> 14:15.120
Before Jiang Cheng came back,

14:15.670 --> 14:16.860
the profile of Qi Yan

14:16.190 --> 14:17.790
[Qi Yan]

14:17.070 --> 14:18.310
never matched the image the police have

14:18.310 --> 14:19.740
of Old Scorpion.

14:20.040 --> 14:25.190
[Qi Yan=Old Scorpion?]

14:20.340 --> 14:21.460
This led everyone

14:21.740 --> 14:22.940
to never suspect

14:23.430 --> 14:25.360
that they could be the same person.

14:25.580 --> 14:26.940
Number 1, 2, and 4.

14:27.550 --> 14:28.550
The rest are fine.

14:29.580 --> 14:30.910
Bring in the next group.

14:31.740 --> 14:33.570
In Jiang Cheng's previous concept,

14:33.570 --> 14:34.600
[Brother]

14:33.740 --> 14:35.620
Old Scorpion was always an old guy.

14:34.600 --> 14:36.460
[Father???]

14:36.620 --> 14:38.820
It shouldn't have been his assumption,

14:38.910 --> 14:40.100
but rather a consensus.

14:40.100 --> 14:41.510
Number 2, 5, 6, and 7.

14:43.700 --> 14:44.790
Number 3 and 5.

14:46.270 --> 14:47.270
Number 2 and 4.

14:47.590 --> 14:49.110
[Drugs] [Killing a Police Officer]

14:47.940 --> 14:49.550
Since Qi Yan never showed himself,

14:49.110 --> 14:50.310
[Revenge]

14:50.030 --> 14:52.070
naturally,
he needs someone to act on his behalf.

14:50.310 --> 14:51.530
[Qi Yan]

14:52.860 --> 14:53.940
This Qi might be

14:53.940 --> 14:55.390
his spokesperson on the surface.

14:55.080 --> 14:56.380
[Qi Yan=Old Scorpion?]

14:56.030 --> 14:57.980
Qi Yan's history
could be erased completely,

14:56.380 --> 14:57.560
[Huaiguang Murder Case—Red Dress, Wrist Slashing, Bow Knot, Oedipus Complex, Misogyny]
[8.17 Case—Drugs, Killing a Police Officer, Sniper, Knife]

14:57.560 --> 14:58.740
[Ningyuan, Haizhou Murder Case—
New Red Dress, New Bow Knot, Needle, Protest]

14:58.550 --> 14:59.580
but this Qi's

14:58.760 --> 15:00.710
[Jingang Wharf—Drugs, Killing a Police Officer, Revenge. Kuangshan—Drug Factory]
[Brother? Father?]

14:59.790 --> 15:00.730
is less likely to be.

15:00.730 --> 15:01.680
[Oedipus Complex, Anti-Police]
[Qi Zhen, Jian Liang]

15:01.790 --> 15:03.430
Finding a flaw in him

15:04.190 --> 15:05.190
should be easier.

15:09.430 --> 15:10.890
Why don't you give Zhou Jin

15:11.470 --> 15:12.400
a call?

15:14.940 --> 15:16.070
I'll call Chief Tan.

15:26.390 --> 15:26.990
Chief Tan.

15:27.460 --> 15:28.700
We found the car that followed Zhou Jin

15:28.700 --> 15:30.100
before her car accident.

15:30.310 --> 15:31.790
It's a car with a fake license plate.

15:31.790 --> 15:33.030
After the accident,

15:33.030 --> 15:34.510
the car kept heading toward
the countryside

15:34.510 --> 15:36.190
and finally stopped by a ditch.

15:36.190 --> 15:37.150
It's quite remote

15:37.150 --> 15:39.350
and there are no surveillance cameras.

16:34.620 --> 16:35.880
I've been here before.

16:39.940 --> 16:42.100
We hid around here
before we entered Kuangshan.

16:42.100 --> 16:43.190
I remember this smell.

16:43.190 --> 16:45.320
It's a stench with a hint of fishiness.

16:46.940 --> 16:48.200
Where were you hiding?

16:49.190 --> 16:50.310
If you look down in this direction,

16:50.310 --> 16:51.620
there should be a village.

16:51.620 --> 16:53.860
There's a house with a bamboo fence,

16:53.860 --> 16:55.660
and the walls are painted green.

16:55.700 --> 16:57.700
It could easily hide a dozen people.

16:57.820 --> 16:58.550
Before entering Kuangshan,

16:58.550 --> 17:00.350
we hid in there for several days.

17:00.430 --> 17:02.030
Although I was blindfolded,

17:02.030 --> 17:03.290
I remember this smell.

17:04.470 --> 17:05.380
If you say

17:05.790 --> 17:07.380
Qi was in this car,

17:07.819 --> 17:08.750
it's possible.

17:09.099 --> 17:10.829
They have a stronghold nearby.

17:12.030 --> 17:12.579
Lu.

17:12.900 --> 17:13.420
Here.

17:13.579 --> 17:15.339
Find a few people to check it out.

17:15.339 --> 17:15.790
Yes.

17:17.420 --> 17:18.619
You two, come with me.

17:24.510 --> 17:25.510
Yes, Director Lu.

17:26.180 --> 17:28.310
If Jiang Cheng's judgment is correct,

17:28.790 --> 17:29.790
we need to

17:29.860 --> 17:30.790
act immediately

17:31.100 --> 17:32.160
and take them down.

17:32.380 --> 17:33.030
Alright.

17:33.140 --> 17:33.940
Let's do this.

17:34.620 --> 17:37.020
Give me the action plan
as soon as possible.

17:37.140 --> 17:37.670
Alright.

17:41.790 --> 17:42.950
The Provincial Bureau agreed.

17:42.950 --> 17:44.280
Act as soon as possible.

17:44.470 --> 17:44.860
Yes.

17:45.660 --> 17:46.710
You go out and wait.

17:46.710 --> 17:48.140
We have things to discuss.

17:48.140 --> 17:48.950
Yes.

17:52.230 --> 17:53.560
Is there anything else?

17:55.510 --> 17:56.510
If we take action,

17:56.510 --> 17:57.640
I have two requests.

17:58.030 --> 17:59.560
I hope you can agree to them.

18:02.310 --> 18:03.640
What are your thoughts?

18:04.070 --> 18:04.990
Tell us.

18:05.470 --> 18:06.030
First,

18:06.140 --> 18:07.400
give me an action team.

18:07.900 --> 18:10.340
I want to lead them personally
to make the arrest.

18:10.340 --> 18:11.200
And the second?

18:11.660 --> 18:13.320
I want Zhou Jin to be my deputy.

18:26.100 --> 18:27.550
I understand your feeling

18:27.550 --> 18:29.790
of wanting to arrest them yourself.

18:30.550 --> 18:31.480
But Jiang Cheng,

18:32.540 --> 18:35.070
you haven't been
officially reinstated yet.

18:35.750 --> 18:37.140
You can at most assist in this operation

18:37.140 --> 18:38.340
as an informed person

18:39.750 --> 18:41.410
familiar with the situation.

18:41.790 --> 18:43.140
As for the second request,

18:43.140 --> 18:44.340
I can have Zhou Jin

18:44.550 --> 18:46.660
be responsible for ensuring your safety.
You'll be in the same team.

18:46.660 --> 18:49.590
Once the exact location
of the hideout is confirmed,

18:50.860 --> 18:52.520
your reconnaissance mission

18:53.030 --> 18:54.090
will be completed.

18:59.620 --> 19:00.180
Okay.

19:00.950 --> 19:01.510
Is that alright?

19:01.510 --> 19:03.310
You still don't trust me, do you?

19:03.380 --> 19:04.180
Jiang Cheng!

19:05.030 --> 19:06.490
This is about discipline!

19:06.710 --> 19:08.840
You must get used to following orders.

19:12.790 --> 19:13.420
Zhou Jin,

19:14.420 --> 19:16.180
the task of protecting him
is assigned to you.

19:16.180 --> 19:17.110
Aside from that,

19:17.580 --> 19:19.710
don't cause any unnecessary trouble.

19:20.100 --> 19:20.580
Yes.

19:22.070 --> 19:22.930
What about you?

19:24.270 --> 19:24.750
Okay.

19:25.140 --> 19:25.580
Okay.

19:26.230 --> 19:27.760
I'll listen to you, Leader.

19:42.990 --> 19:43.230
Come on.

19:43.230 --> 19:45.070
You're working for such a rigid person?

19:45.070 --> 19:47.470
He doesn't even fight
for his subordinates?

19:47.470 --> 19:49.070
Don't speak ill of my mentor.

19:49.750 --> 19:50.660
It seems he treats you well.

19:50.660 --> 19:51.920
You quite respect him.

19:54.620 --> 19:55.680
What are you doing?

19:59.860 --> 20:01.520
Reporting to Jiang Hansheng?

20:02.790 --> 20:03.620
He doesn't seem

20:03.620 --> 20:04.900
to be very confident.

20:04.900 --> 20:05.510
Can he handle

20:05.510 --> 20:07.110
you provoking him like this?

20:09.180 --> 20:11.180
Wei asked me if you were reinstated.

20:14.550 --> 20:15.350
He's calling.

20:17.070 --> 20:17.710
Wei.

20:18.070 --> 20:18.860
Jin,

20:19.230 --> 20:20.490
are you busy right now?

20:21.470 --> 20:22.270
Hello.

20:23.030 --> 20:24.380
Seeing you in this uniform

20:24.380 --> 20:25.660
puts my mind at ease.

20:26.180 --> 20:27.840
Yet you never came to visit me.

20:28.620 --> 20:29.820
I've been in meetings every day recently.

20:29.820 --> 20:30.620
I'm too busy.

20:31.230 --> 20:32.990
What have you guys been busy with lately?

20:32.990 --> 20:35.450
You never reply to my messages
immediately.

20:35.510 --> 20:36.510
Are you that busy?

20:36.790 --> 20:37.580
We are indeed busy.

20:37.580 --> 20:39.380
We also just got out of a meeting.

20:39.420 --> 20:40.620
Looks like

20:40.660 --> 20:42.310
you were fighting side by side.

20:42.310 --> 20:43.620
I'm happy for you.

20:45.100 --> 20:46.950
I also have some good news to tell you.

20:46.950 --> 20:49.070
Do you have any free time
these next few days

20:49.070 --> 20:50.270
to come to Jingzhou and attend

20:50.270 --> 20:52.400
my son's one-month birthday banquet?

20:53.030 --> 20:55.630
I'll definitely come
if I don't have a mission.

20:55.660 --> 20:57.420
I'm not going.

20:57.420 --> 20:58.510
I can't leave Haizhou.

20:58.510 --> 20:59.790
I'm still in the evaluation period.

20:59.790 --> 21:01.050
Jin will represent me.

21:01.140 --> 21:01.860
Jin,

21:02.310 --> 21:04.040
are you bringing your husband?

21:05.660 --> 21:06.990
I'll go ask Hansheng.

21:07.660 --> 21:08.270
Okay.

21:08.820 --> 21:11.510
I happen to have some work-related matters

21:11.510 --> 21:13.510
I'd like to consult Professor Jiang about.

21:13.510 --> 21:15.710
Then I'll try my best
to get him to go too.

21:17.710 --> 21:19.310
Okay, there's nothing else.

21:21.270 --> 21:22.070
Jiang Cheng.

21:22.660 --> 21:25.270
How about we find some free time
in the next couple of days

21:25.270 --> 21:26.140
to get together?

21:26.140 --> 21:27.470
He went to the restroom.

21:29.380 --> 21:29.990
Jin,

21:30.820 --> 21:31.790
seeing you again,

21:31.790 --> 21:33.470
he must have mixed feelings.

21:34.510 --> 21:36.510
You should change how you interact.

21:36.820 --> 21:37.880
Don't be too stiff,

21:38.070 --> 21:39.070
and don't rush it.

21:39.070 --> 21:39.860
I know.

21:40.670 --> 21:41.710
It's hard.

21:43.180 --> 21:43.990
I understand.

21:45.470 --> 21:46.530
It will get better.

21:48.510 --> 21:49.110
Oh, right.

21:49.480 --> 21:51.750
For your son's one-month birthday banquet,

21:51.750 --> 21:53.750
will our former SWAT colleagues go?

21:55.000 --> 21:56.680
Some of them from back then
were restructured,

21:56.680 --> 21:58.140
and some were reassigned.

21:58.270 --> 21:59.870
Now they're all busy people,

22:00.270 --> 22:02.310
so they might not make the time to attend.

22:02.310 --> 22:03.110
What's wrong?

22:04.510 --> 22:06.880
I'm thinking they might know my brother.

22:07.720 --> 22:10.650
We could probably talk about him
if we see each other.

22:11.000 --> 22:12.550
You're missing you brother?

22:12.550 --> 22:14.680
It must be because of the recent cases.

22:16.030 --> 22:16.680
Wei,

22:17.480 --> 22:18.880
do you and your wife

22:19.510 --> 22:21.110
still talk about my brother?

22:22.200 --> 22:22.880
Rarely.

22:23.680 --> 22:25.540
Then does she still remember him?

22:25.550 --> 22:26.750
Of course she does.

22:27.550 --> 22:29.880
He was her idol back then.

22:33.960 --> 22:35.000
Did...

22:36.920 --> 22:39.120
Did my brother have any enemies before?

22:40.830 --> 22:42.560
What enemies could Cheng have?

22:42.880 --> 22:45.010
Why do you suddenly have this thought?

22:45.960 --> 22:46.760
It's nothing.

22:47.480 --> 22:48.810
Let's talk when we meet.

22:49.310 --> 22:49.750
Okay.

22:50.550 --> 22:51.610
I'm hanging up now.

23:47.790 --> 23:48.520
Jiang Cheng.

23:50.200 --> 23:51.400
You're done talking?

23:51.960 --> 23:53.960
Why didn't you talk to Wei a bit more?

23:54.000 --> 23:56.310
We are grown men.
We don't have that much to say.

23:56.310 --> 23:57.110
Mentor told us

23:57.270 --> 23:58.480
to wait for his next instruction

23:58.480 --> 23:59.750
and stand by at all times.

23:59.750 --> 24:00.280
Let's go.

24:00.720 --> 24:01.240
Okay.

24:01.680 --> 24:03.740
You didn't even wipe your face clean.

24:10.200 --> 24:11.000
Look at this.

24:13.440 --> 24:14.790
Is it a new clue?

24:15.270 --> 24:16.350
Not really new.

24:17.590 --> 24:19.640
Do you remember the guy who took the fall

24:19.640 --> 24:20.880
for the Huaiguang Case?

24:20.880 --> 24:22.830
It's the materials I collected about him.

24:22.830 --> 24:23.640
Chen Li?

24:23.880 --> 24:24.880
That accountant?

24:25.000 --> 24:25.790
Yes.

24:26.960 --> 24:28.550
Is there any new progress?

24:32.590 --> 24:34.050
Chen Li's ex-wife is back.

24:43.590 --> 24:44.320
Jiang Cheng,

24:44.640 --> 24:45.970
we trust your judgment.

24:46.270 --> 24:47.270
Just do your best.

24:48.030 --> 24:48.960
You may proceed.

24:53.830 --> 24:55.200
First, drive along this road.

24:55.200 --> 24:56.200
Keep the speed...

24:56.200 --> 24:57.160
at 40.

24:57.400 --> 24:57.830
Okay.

25:26.310 --> 25:27.550
About 50 meters ahead,

25:27.550 --> 25:29.080
there's a left turn, right?

25:30.240 --> 25:30.720
Yes.

25:31.400 --> 25:32.000
Turn left.

25:32.510 --> 25:32.960
Okay.

25:38.670 --> 25:40.580
[Pond] [Stinky ditch]

25:58.960 --> 26:00.220
Stop here for a second.

26:21.790 --> 26:23.550
When we got near here that day,

26:24.830 --> 26:26.310
I smelled burning incense.

26:26.310 --> 26:27.310
Burning incense?

26:27.400 --> 26:27.750
Yes.

26:35.070 --> 26:36.070
Command vehicle!

26:36.070 --> 26:37.030
Copy, go ahead.

26:37.240 --> 26:38.070
Help me check

26:38.070 --> 26:40.530
if there's any place
to burn incense nearby.

26:40.640 --> 26:41.590
For example,

26:41.830 --> 26:42.880
an Earth God temple

26:42.880 --> 26:44.080
or an ancestral hall.

26:45.590 --> 26:47.240
There's a tiny Earth God temple.

26:47.240 --> 26:48.640
Go straight for about 40 meters,

26:48.640 --> 26:50.300
turn right, and you'll see it.

26:50.790 --> 26:51.390
Copy that.

27:22.680 --> 27:23.590
It's not far now.

27:23.590 --> 27:25.960
Go down this road
for about 500 or 600 meters,

27:25.960 --> 27:27.720
and there's a farmhouse.

27:27.750 --> 27:29.310
It's isolated, with no neighbors.

27:29.310 --> 27:30.790
It's the one I told you about yesterday,

27:30.790 --> 27:32.550
the small yard with the bamboo fence.

27:32.550 --> 27:34.080
Wait a minute. Let me check.

27:40.110 --> 27:40.720
Found it.

27:41.350 --> 27:42.510
Send it to the action team.

27:42.510 --> 27:43.000
Yes.

27:44.270 --> 27:45.160
Well done, Jiang Cheng.

27:45.160 --> 27:46.620
Your mission is complete.

28:12.070 --> 28:13.790
Are there any extra walkie-talkies
in the car?

28:13.790 --> 28:14.830
Yes.

28:15.110 --> 28:16.840
Bring one over. Mine is broken.

28:17.550 --> 28:18.400
Coming.

28:26.010 --> 28:28.600
[Police]

28:42.800 --> 28:44.120
[SWAT]

28:45.920 --> 28:46.400
Report.

28:46.720 --> 28:48.110
We have surrounded the target courtyard,

28:48.110 --> 28:49.880
but there are 3 entrances
at the front and back.

28:49.880 --> 28:51.750
We cannot further investigate
the situation inside.

28:51.750 --> 28:52.880
Please give orders.

28:55.550 --> 28:56.310
Take action.

28:56.830 --> 28:57.270
Yes.

29:08.720 --> 29:10.320
I know what you're thinking.

29:14.400 --> 29:15.400
But it's the rule.

29:17.720 --> 29:19.160
No need to remind me.

29:20.750 --> 29:21.550
I understand.

29:22.160 --> 29:24.620
I'm just assisting with the investigation.

29:40.960 --> 29:41.620
Godfather,

29:41.680 --> 29:42.270
please,

29:42.440 --> 29:43.770
give me one last chance.

29:44.030 --> 29:45.590
No wonder you kept making mistakes

29:45.590 --> 29:48.070
and bringing me bad luck
for the past year and a half.

29:48.070 --> 29:49.680
Turns out you're a mole.

30:00.640 --> 30:01.510
Well...

30:02.590 --> 30:03.720
Yao Weihai...

30:05.350 --> 30:06.680
I'll leave him to you.

30:06.960 --> 30:07.690
Understood.

30:08.000 --> 30:09.460
Thanks for your hard work.

30:12.200 --> 30:13.030
Alright.

30:13.440 --> 30:15.170
The mole has been taken care of.

30:15.720 --> 30:17.250
And my mission is complete.

30:17.790 --> 30:18.960
Next step...

30:20.030 --> 30:20.790
Jiang Cheng,

30:21.750 --> 30:22.960
prove yourself.

30:26.110 --> 30:26.960
I get it.

30:27.720 --> 30:28.850
A pledge of loyalty.

30:50.590 --> 30:51.790
At a 45-degree angle.

30:52.680 --> 30:53.960
Against the head.

31:08.030 --> 31:09.790
You used to be a cop.

31:10.680 --> 31:12.590
Do you dare to kill one?

31:13.680 --> 31:15.070
Why wouldn't I dare?

31:16.750 --> 31:18.640
Then do it.

31:20.200 --> 31:21.920
The sun is almost up.

31:31.880 --> 31:33.960
Before his last mission,

31:35.310 --> 31:37.200
he asked me to get him

31:38.000 --> 31:38.660
one of those

31:38.790 --> 31:40.440
little cyanide capsules.

31:41.590 --> 31:43.520
He said the mission was dangerous,

31:44.200 --> 31:45.660
and it might come in handy.

31:58.110 --> 31:59.110
No matter how hard

31:59.720 --> 32:00.780
or dangerous it is,

32:01.750 --> 32:02.410
I accept it.

32:29.160 --> 32:30.000
Jiang Cheng,

32:30.680 --> 32:32.340
you really didn't let me down.

32:33.200 --> 32:35.200
How could I let you pull the trigger?

32:35.440 --> 32:37.040
After all, you saved my life.

32:42.920 --> 32:44.920
Didn't you want to see Old Scorpion?

32:46.960 --> 32:48.480
You'll see him soon.

33:06.550 --> 33:07.310
Jiang Cheng.

33:10.270 --> 33:11.160
What's wrong?

33:17.480 --> 33:18.400
Jin,

33:19.000 --> 33:21.400
sometimes living is harder than dying.

33:21.550 --> 33:22.510
You know?

33:25.270 --> 33:27.640
Bearing all the trust alone,

33:27.640 --> 33:29.440
yet being unable to do anything.

33:32.000 --> 33:34.200
Whenever I think of Yao's last moments,

33:34.920 --> 33:37.480
and that Meng Junfeng died for me,

33:38.680 --> 33:40.440
I feel like even taking a breath

33:41.200 --> 33:42.880
is wrong.

33:44.200 --> 33:45.350
No.

33:47.680 --> 33:48.880
It's not like that.

33:53.510 --> 33:54.200
Jin,

33:55.830 --> 33:57.560
I must get this revenge myself.

33:58.310 --> 34:00.170
If I don't go and atone for my sins,

34:01.270 --> 34:03.000
I will never forgive myself.

34:11.440 --> 34:13.030
Jin, untie me!

34:13.670 --> 34:14.360
Jin!

34:14.630 --> 34:15.800
Didn't you hear what I said?

34:15.800 --> 34:16.880
If I don't get this revenge,

34:16.880 --> 34:18.320
I won't be at peace!

34:18.480 --> 34:19.400
Shut up!

34:20.030 --> 34:21.590
If you do something stupid again,

34:21.590 --> 34:23.110
I will never forgive you!

34:31.190 --> 34:32.920
I've already lost one brother.

34:36.760 --> 34:38.760
I can't lose another family member.

34:57.710 --> 34:59.440
Why are you always so mean to me?

35:00.110 --> 35:02.440
Are you like this with Jiang Hansheng too?

35:04.710 --> 35:05.970
None of your business.

35:24.670 --> 35:25.480
Professor Jiang.

35:25.480 --> 35:28.480
Zhou Jin participated in
today's capture operation?

35:28.590 --> 35:29.520
How did you know?

35:31.440 --> 35:32.500
I'll be there soon.

35:32.670 --> 35:34.070
Are you going to the scene?

35:34.070 --> 35:35.000
Qi Yan knows her.

35:35.630 --> 35:36.890
I'm worried about her.

35:37.550 --> 35:39.280
You don't need to worry too much.

35:39.280 --> 35:41.110
Zhou Jin is just
in the Surveillance team this time.

35:41.110 --> 35:42.760
She's not directly participating
in the operation.

35:42.760 --> 35:43.670
She should be

35:43.960 --> 35:44.960
very safe now.

35:45.630 --> 35:48.090
I need to see with my own eyes
that she's safe.

35:54.710 --> 35:55.590
Command vehicle.

35:55.590 --> 35:56.630
The scene is basically under control.

35:56.630 --> 35:58.070
But we didn't see the prime suspect.

35:58.070 --> 35:59.150
Please pay attention to the perimeter.

35:59.150 --> 36:00.760
Maybe the prime suspect has escaped

36:00.760 --> 36:01.880
from a blind spot.

36:04.150 --> 36:05.610
Old Scorpion isn't there?

36:06.480 --> 36:07.150
Qi Yan,

36:07.150 --> 36:07.670
Qi,

36:07.670 --> 36:08.230
and Qiu Ye—

36:08.230 --> 36:09.360
none of them is here.

36:09.760 --> 36:11.280
Attention,
perimeter reconnaissance vehicles.

36:11.280 --> 36:13.230
See if any suspicious persons escaped.

36:13.230 --> 36:14.800
The prime suspect is still at large.

36:14.800 --> 36:16.260
No traces have been found.

36:16.880 --> 36:17.590
Copy that.

36:25.550 --> 36:26.190
Jin,

36:26.280 --> 36:27.030
untie me.

36:27.670 --> 36:28.230
Jin.

36:28.630 --> 36:30.230
Hurry! Unlock my handcuffs!

36:30.400 --> 36:30.960
Jin!

36:31.190 --> 36:31.840
Jin!

36:32.230 --> 36:33.840
Don't go alone, Jin!

36:35.710 --> 36:36.280
Jin!

36:36.760 --> 36:37.510
Jin!

36:42.440 --> 36:43.920
Chief Tan, suspects found here.

36:43.920 --> 36:44.760
Requesting backup.

36:44.400 --> 36:46.050
[Police]

36:46.110 --> 36:47.150
Stop! Don't run!

36:59.320 --> 37:00.550
Two men, armed.

37:01.070 --> 37:02.600
They got into a black sedan.

37:08.590 --> 37:09.440
Black Chevrolet,

37:09.440 --> 37:10.280
65K51.

37:14.070 --> 37:14.840
Don't be scared!

37:14.840 --> 37:16.240
Drive straight through!

37:37.590 --> 37:38.390
Hold on tight!

37:41.510 --> 37:42.040
Zhou Jin.

37:42.320 --> 37:44.000
Hansheng and I are driving to chase them.

37:44.000 --> 37:45.190
They are in our sight,

37:45.190 --> 37:46.510
heading down the mountain road.

37:46.510 --> 37:47.670
Stay on the suspects.

37:47.670 --> 37:48.800
Backup is on the way.

38:31.550 --> 38:32.280
Stop the car!

38:32.360 --> 38:33.190
Stop resisting!

38:33.190 --> 38:33.840
Hit him!

38:34.920 --> 38:35.550
Hit him!

38:39.070 --> 38:39.870
Hold on tight.

38:48.880 --> 38:50.010
Floor the gas pedal!

38:50.440 --> 38:51.960
Floor it!

38:57.230 --> 38:58.890
I guess we've made up now, huh?

39:06.150 --> 39:06.880
Stop the car!

39:35.480 --> 39:36.210
Stop the car!

39:51.960 --> 39:53.160
Don't turn the wheel!

39:53.630 --> 39:54.960
Let's all die together!

41:14.630 --> 41:15.400
Zhou Jin...

41:39.670 --> 41:40.920
-Junior!
-Zhou!

41:41.150 --> 41:41.760
Zhou!

41:42.030 --> 41:43.320
Open the door! Open it!

41:44.190 --> 41:45.280
Junior, wake up!

41:45.280 --> 41:46.280
Zhou, wake up!

41:46.960 --> 41:47.690
Pull harder!

41:51.000 --> 41:51.800
Zhou!

41:54.280 --> 41:55.150
Junior, wake up!

41:55.150 --> 41:55.960
Zhou, wake up.

41:55.960 --> 41:56.880
Junior, wake up!

41:56.880 --> 41:58.480
I will never nag you again, Junior!

41:58.480 --> 41:59.810
-Zhou.
-Junior Sister!

42:00.920 --> 42:01.800
Zhou?

42:02.000 --> 42:03.200
Junior, are you okay?

42:03.480 --> 42:04.630
How do you feel?

42:05.590 --> 42:06.320
How do you feel?

42:06.320 --> 42:07.070
How do you feel?

42:07.070 --> 42:07.880
I'm fine.

42:08.280 --> 42:09.190
Are you alright?

42:09.190 --> 42:10.990
I-I'll get you some water, okay?

42:11.230 --> 42:12.670
-Come on.
-Be careful.

42:16.320 --> 42:17.520
I'm glad you're okay.

42:17.630 --> 42:20.090
Wan,
what's the situation at the scene like?

42:20.400 --> 42:21.510
Qi has been arrested.

42:21.510 --> 42:23.040
The scene is under control.

42:23.440 --> 42:24.320
But there are people injured.

42:24.320 --> 42:25.720
We need medical support.

42:27.880 --> 42:29.030
Medical team! Medical team!
